{"word":"G2284 - θαμβέω - thambéō - tham-beh'-o - Amaze","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θαμβέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thambéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tham-beh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Amaze</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆச்சரியப்படு, திகை"},{"paragraph":"1. to be astonished"},{"paragraph":"2. to astonish, terrify"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2285 - θάμβος - thámbos - tham'-bos/2285\">G2285</a>; to <i>stupefy</i> (with surprise), that is, <i>astound:</i> - amaze, astonish.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1568/1568\">G1568</a>, <a href=\"#/G1569/1569\">G1569</a>, <a href=\"#/G2284/2284\">G2284</a>, <a href=\"#/G2285/2285\">G2285</a>"}]}